<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>come into the limelight • come to light</xh5><p> <i>come into the limelight—</i>be in the center of attention: The giant Himalayan humanoid <u>came into the limelight</u> in 1921 and has since been the subject of much controversy.</p><p> <i>come to light—</i>be revealed; become known: From the stones, ice and meadows of Greenland the tragic story of the lost Vikings has finally <u>come to light</u>.</p> </entry>
